===Speak with the little robot and plan your route from here{{subst:void|<!--200140101-->}}===
{{Mission Description|type=adventure|location=Silvermane Guard Restricted Zone|According to the little robot's navigation route, the next stop is Aurum Alley on the Luofu.}}
