;(Talk to Little Robot)
:'''Little Robot:''' According to the data provided by Miss Himeko, the Astral Express has stopped in the Luofu's Aurum Alley previously, and served to revitalize the local industries.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} That's right. I chased out the IPC dogs myself.
::'''Little Robot:''' Strictly speaking, I am a product developed by the IPC. Though I do not resemble a dog on the exterior, I would ask you not to chase me away.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Then what are we waiting for? Let's get going!
::'''Little Robot:''' One moment. My database is showing that there is a second destination.
:'''Little Robot:''' We must visit the Alchemy Commission as well as Aurum Alley. The Nameless had assisted Yueyuan of the Vidyadhara in the past, though I am currently unable to contact her.
:'''Little Robot:''' So, our next journey will be &mdash; To Du's Teahouse in Aurum Alley to meet with Boss Du.
:'''Little Robot:''' As for the Alchemy Commission, I have left a word with Yueyuan. Please wait for her to reply.
{{Dialogue End}}

