===Go to the Alchemy Commission and speak with Yueyuan{{subst:void|<!--200140105-->}}===
{{Dialogue Start}}

;(Talk to Yueyuan)
:'''Yueyuan:''' Here's what is written in the letter if you'd like to read it. I don't know if the writer's imagination has run away with them, or if they just have too much time on their hands.
:It looks like the previous story of being lost at sea has come to an end. It seems the author has taken a new artistic direction.
<pre>{
	"$type": "RPG.GameCore.ShowReading",
	"BookID": {
		"FixedValue": {
			"Value": 190764
		}
	}
