:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I imagine that's the end of the Drift Bottles.
::'''Yueyuan:''' I hope so. I've had enough of these twists and turns.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} He's moved on to science-fiction.
::'''Yueyuan:''' A stellar winds balloon... Just how many ludicrous ideas can one person have in their head?
::'''Yueyuan:''' It wasn't enough for him to pollute the oceans, now he's throwing his trash into the Cosmos?
:'''Yueyuan:''' Whatever the case, it looks like this whole thing has finally come to an end. Thank you for your hard work back then.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} You won't need me to go on patrols anymore?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Huh? That's it? Just "Thank you for your hard work"?
:'''Yueyuan:''' I don't need to trouble you with all this anymore. I have bought a batch of cycranes that will do daily patrols and other missions like this.
:'''Yueyuan:''' Naturally, in recognition of your outstanding contributions to the environmental protection of the Lunarescent Depths, I have applied for you to receive a special reward from the Realm-Keeping Commission. The application should be approved soon.
:'''Little Robot:''' All to-do items have been completed. You can prepare for your return when you are ready.
:'''Little Robot:''' Beep beep beep &mdash; it is time to return and charge my batteries.
:'''Yueyuan:''' Oh? You're leaving? Alright, if you wish to come and visit me at the seaside, you are welcome any time.
{{Dialogue End}}

